    <a href="{{unsubscribe-exp-this-token-url}}">{{unsubscribe-exp-this-token-url}}</a>
</p>

<p>
    If you want to manage the whole notification subscription, you can do so at:
    <a href="{{management-url}}">{{management-url}}</a>
